<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·豳风·破斧</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson1f7e5dfe2da1">
<p>既破我斧，又缺我斨。周公东征，四国是皇。哀我人斯，亦孔之将。<br />既破我斧，又缺我锜。周公东征，四国是吪。哀我人斯，亦孔之嘉。<br />既破我斧，又缺我銶。周公东征，四国是遒。哀我人斯，亦孔之休。</p>
</div>
</div>
